Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,召集大军 时候到了\N{\fs16}Summon the legions. It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们的敌人誓要进攻\N{\fs16}Our enemy vows to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你们谁愿意挺身一战？\N{\fs16}Who among you will stand and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:15.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你们会死的\N{\fs16}You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我等待这一天很久了\N{\fs16}<i>Long have I awaited this day.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我向索隆宣誓效忠\N{\fs16}I pledge my loyalty to Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们一半的人都走了\N{\fs16}Half of us just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:25.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,但还有一半选择留下\N{\fs16}But half stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.05,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我怎么没被选中参加远征？\N{\fs16}<i>Why wasn't I chosen for the expedition?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你不是想往西去嘛\N{\fs16}Thought you were going west.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我得先做点什么 尽忠于努门诺尔\N{\fs16}Not till I've done something worthy of Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我刚说服了努门诺尔派出五艘船\N{\fs16}<i>I have just convinced Númenor to send five ships</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,五百精锐 援助你的人民\N{\fs16}<i>and 500 men to aid your people</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,助你加冕为王\N{\fs16}<i>and place a crown upon your head.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你要让我去一个我曾发誓不会再去的地方\N{\fs16}You are asking me to go to the one place that I swore never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:43.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你为何依旧战斗？\N{\fs16}Why do you keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:45.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,因为我无法停下\N{\fs16}Because I cannot stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:49.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,跟我走 我们将合力拯救各自的血脉\N{\fs16}<i>Come with me, and together we will redeem both our bloodlines.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们朝东北行进\N{\fs16}We head nor'-east.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:55.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,前往中洲\N{\fs16}For Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:59.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,那可不是剑 是种力量\N{\fs16}<i>It is no sword. It is a power.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:01.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,听说过索隆吗?\N{\fs16}Have you heard of Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我曾见过它\N{\fs16}<i>I've seen this before.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这是把钥匙\N{\fs16}<i>It is a key.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,大敌以失传法术所制 用于奴役你的先祖\N{\fs16}<i>The enemy commander spoke of giving the Orcs a home in these lands.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,但不论他有何企图 毋庸置疑的是\N{\fs16}<i>Whatever his design, this much is certain.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:15.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,敌人知道你儿子有他启动计划所需的东西\N{\fs16}<i>Our enemy knows your son has what he needs to enact it.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,还有多久?\N{\fs16}<i>How long?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:19.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,也许几小时\N{\fs16}<i>Maybe hours.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:27.58,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,以新生\N{\fs16}<i>Vinya coivie</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.00,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,对抗死亡\N{\fs16}<i>nat fírie.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我的孩子们\N{\fs16}My children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:56.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们历经无数艰辛\N{\fs16}we have endured much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:04.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们挣脱了枷锁\N{\fs16}We cast off our shackles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,跨过高山和田野\N{\fs16}Crossed mountain, field,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,穿越严寒与荒地\N{\fs16}frost, and fallow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,直到脚上的血浸染了泥土\N{\fs16}till our feet bloodied the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:22.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,从埃瑞德米斯林到埃斐尔阿尔能\N{\fs16}From <i>Ered Mithrin</i> to the <i>Ephel Arnen,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们都挺过来了\N{\fs16}we have endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:35.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,然而今晚 还有一场考验等待着我们\N{\fs16}Yet tonight, one more trial awaits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:41.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们的敌人可能势单力薄\N{\fs16}Our enemy may be weak, their numbers meager...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:48.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,但在今夜结束之前 我们中有些会倒下\N{\fs16}...yet before this night is through, some of us will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,然而这一次 当你们倒下时\N{\fs16}But for the first time, you do so
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:58.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,将不再是远方大地上的无名奴隶\N{\fs16}not as unnamed slaves in far-away lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,而是彼此的兄弟\N{\fs16}but as brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,以兄弟姐妹的身份 在家园的土地上倒下！\N{\fs16}As brothers and sisters in our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,战斗\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,战斗！战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat! Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.44,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,就在今晚\N{\fs16}This is the night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:17.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-我们伸出乌鲁克族的铁拳 -战斗！战斗！\N{\fs16}- we reach out the iron hand of the <i>Uruk... - Nampat! Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,握紧拳头夺回这片土地\N{\fs16}...and close our fist around these lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,给我搜\N{\fs16}Search it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:17.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,全体注意！分头行动！找到他们！\N{\fs16}All of you! Fan out! Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,无意顶撞 父亲大人 但他在哪？\N{\fs16}Meaning no offense, Lord-father, but where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,索隆出什么事了？\N{\fs16}What happened to Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:13.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,找不到他的行踪轨迹 肯定是学聪明溜走了\N{\fs16}Can't find tooth nor tail of him. Must've got smart and scarpered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不 那个精灵就在这里\N{\fs16}No. The Elf's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我闻到了他的气味\N{\fs16}I smell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,遵命 父亲\N{\fs16}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,在这上面！\N{\fs16}Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,拿下他！\N{\fs16}Bring him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,出去 快点！\N{\fs16}Get out, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,打开那扇门！\N{\fs16}Open that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,快出去！\N{\fs16}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,父亲大人！您得马上离开！\N{\fs16}Lord-father! You must move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,您得离开！\N{\fs16}You must move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,有几个挨了这一下还能活下来？\N{\fs16}How many of 'em could have survived that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们还有多少时间？\N{\fs16}How long do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,没多少了\N{\fs16}Not long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,来吧 我们必须做好准备\N{\fs16}Come on, we have to make ready the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,别紧张 贝瑞克 放松\N{\fs16}Easy, Berek. Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,升帆！\N{\fs16}Hoist it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我以为现在是全体士兵的就寝时间\N{\fs16}I thought all soldiers were to be abed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,对不起 指挥官 我 我只是…\N{\fs16}Pardon me, Commander. I... I was only...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,想第一个看到陆地？\N{\fs16}Hoping to get the first sight of land?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,稍息\N{\fs16}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:17.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,过一会儿你们就看得到了\N{\fs16}It'll be visible to your eyes in a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,您已经看到了吗？\N{\fs16}Is it visible to yours already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,一小时前就看到了\N{\fs16}Has been for nearly an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,精灵的眼睛真是敏锐\N{\fs16}Keen are the eyes of the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:30.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,可我还从未见过你\N{\fs16}And yet, mine have not before seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你既不使剑又不挂帆\N{\fs16}Swinging steel nor flying sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你是什么军衔？\N{\fs16}What is your rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,扫马厩的\N{\fs16}Stable sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不要轻视使心灵谦卑的劳动\N{\fs16}Despise not the labor which humbles the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,谦卑曾拯救诸多王国 骄傲却只能致其覆灭\N{\fs16}Humility has saved entire kingdoms the proud have all but led to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我加入此次远征可不是来学会谦卑的 指挥官\N{\fs16}I did not join this expedition to be humbled, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,那是为了什么 士兵？\N{\fs16}Then for what did you join, soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我只是想逃走\N{\fs16}I was just trying to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,离那里越远越好\N{\fs16}As far as I could from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,努门诺尔？\N{\fs16}Númenor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,它不是努门诺尔\N{\fs16}It's not Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,反正不是真正的努门诺尔\N{\fs16}Not the real Númenor, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,如果它真的存在过\N{\fs16}If it ever existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,它当然存在过\N{\fs16}It existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,它依然存在\N{\fs16}It exists still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,即便是在最卑微的马厩清扫者心中\N{\fs16}If only in the heart of the lowliest stable sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我是伊熙尔杜\N{\fs16}It's Isildur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我本该知道的\N{\fs16}I might have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你与你父亲容貌相似\N{\fs16}You have the look of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,人们总是说我更像母亲\N{\fs16}I was always told I look more like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,士兵\N{\fs16}Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fs16}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他的母亲\N{\fs16}His mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,她怎么了？\N{\fs16}What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,真是奇怪\N{\fs16}It is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:22.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我此前半生 总是东望旭日跃于海面\N{\fs16}Most of my life, I've looked east to see the Sun rise over the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,西观落日沉入远山\N{\fs16}And west to see it set over the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们正驶入黎明 然而 对我而言\N{\fs16}We're sailing into the dawn, and yet, to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,感觉却像夜幕降临\N{\fs16}it feels like the coming of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,她溺水而死\N{\fs16}She drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,看到陆地了 陛下\N{\fs16}<i>Land has been sighted, Your Majesty.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.17,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,还有多久可以下锚？\N{\fs16}<i>How long before we make anchor?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,要抵达山脉还有一整天的航程\N{\fs16}It's a full day's sail into the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:05.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,从那里出发 还需向东骑行一天到达山谷\N{\fs16}And from there, another day's ride east into the vale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,给其他船只发信号\N{\fs16}Signal the other ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,告诉他们全速前进\N{\fs16}Tell them to make all possible haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们无法摧毁它\N{\fs16}It is beyond our skill to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你要把它藏到哪里？\N{\fs16}Where will you hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不能让任何人知道\N{\fs16}No one must know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,连你也不行\N{\fs16}Not even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们已经发现敌人\N{\fs16}<i>Our enemy has been sighted.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们曾从他们手中逃过一劫\N{\fs16}<i>We survived them before.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,现在我们也要如此\N{\fs16}<i>Now we must do so again.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,就在今晚\N{\fs16}Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们占据了地利\N{\fs16}Our position gives us an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,但若想利用它 就必须诱敌深入\N{\fs16}<i>But to use it, we must draw the enemy in close.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们必须等所有奥克跨过那座桥\N{\fs16}We must wait until every last Orc
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,再发起进攻\N{\fs16}has crossed that bridge to spring our attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这对你们的勇气是个考验\N{\fs16}<i>This will test your nerve.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,沉住气\N{\fs16}<i>Let it.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,所有无法战斗的人员都要在里面驻守\N{\fs16}All who cannot fight will be barricaded inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的要塞 我们的最后据点\N{\fs16}This is to be our keep. Our fallback point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,所有人 振作起来\N{\fs16}Take heart. All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:22.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我见过更单薄的兵力在更悬殊的场合取胜\N{\fs16}I have seen smaller armies defeat greater foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不久 日落将至\N{\fs16}Soon, the sun will set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:30.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,诸位各尽所能 我保证 你们还能看到旭日重升\N{\fs16}Do your part, and I swear to you, you shall see it rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-你们有信心吗？-有\N{\fs16}- Do you believe it? - Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-有信心吗？-有！\N{\fs16}- Do you believe it? - Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,各就各位\N{\fs16}To your positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我呢？\N{\fs16}What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,去酒馆\N{\fs16}Tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,酒馆是留给伤患和孩童的 我能战斗\N{\fs16}Tavern's for wounded and children. I can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我知道你能\N{\fs16}I know you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,所以我要你待在那里 保护不能战斗的人\N{\fs16}Which is why I need you in there, protecting those who cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs16}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:15.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,还记得我小时候 常做噩梦吗？\N{\fs16}Remember when I was little... When I used to have bad dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我记得\N{\fs16}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你还记得你以前说的吗？\N{\fs16}You remember what you used to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,当你在黑暗中抱着我的时候？\N{\fs16}When you would hold me in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,现在可以再说给我听听吗？\N{\fs16}Would you say it to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:37.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,魔影终归只是渺小之物  且会逝去\N{\fs16}"""In the end, this shadow is but a small and passing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,而在魔影无法触及之处\N{\fs16}"""There is light and high beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,光明与崇高的美永存\N{\fs16}"""forever beyond its reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,去寻找光明吧\N{\fs16}"""Find the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,如此魔影便永远不得临身\N{\fs16}"""And the shadow will not find you.""
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,再会 母亲\N{\fs16}Farewell, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗\N{\fs16}<i>Are you ready?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,没有 你呢\N{\fs16}No. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,阿尔费琳种子\N{\fs16}The <i>alfirin</i> seeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这是精灵的一项传统\N{\fs16}It is a tradition among Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:00.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,在上战场前 种下一颗\N{\fs16}Before the battle begins, plant one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,以新生 对抗死亡？\N{\fs16}New life, in defiance of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们相信有一位维拉\N{\fs16}It is believed that one of the Valar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,照看一切生长之物\N{\fs16}watches over growing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,以及播种照料它们的人\N{\fs16}And those who tend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,剩下的种子\N{\fs16}The rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们等战争结束后再种吧\N{\fs16}we shall plant after the battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,在新生的花园里\N{\fs16}In a new garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\fs16}You and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,还有希奥\N{\fs16}And Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们一起\N{\fs16}Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,答应我\N{\fs16}Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fs16}They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,老天啊\N{\fs16}Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:16.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这群待宰的蠢货没击中我们\N{\fs16}The bleeding fools missed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.33,0:23:47.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,冲啊！\N{\fs16}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:51.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他们往酒馆那边去了\N{\fs16}They're headed for the tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:13.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-为了南境而战！-为了南境而战！\N{\fs16}- Fight for the Southlands! - Fight for the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:22.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这片土地是我们的！\N{\fs16}The land is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.25,0:27:35.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,英勇可嘉 精灵 简直万夫莫当\N{\fs16}More than a bit brave, Elf. More than a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.37,0:28:20.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,布隆玟\N{\fs16}Bronwyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.50,0:29:13.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们是在和自己人作战\N{\fs16}We were fighting our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.54,0:29:20.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你以为我们会白白收留他们？\N{\fs16}Thought we'd take 'em in for nothin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.29,0:29:23.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这可是有代价的\N{\fs16}Had to pay the toll...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.41,0:29:29.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,现在 你们都要付出代价了\N{\fs16}And now, all of you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.16,0:29:49.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,特雷德威尔！\N{\fs16}Tredwill!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.75,0:30:13.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,妈妈！\N{\fs16}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.58,0:30:19.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,所有人 躲进要塞！\N{\fs16}Everyone, to the keep!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.20,0:30:22.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,跑！快跑！\N{\fs16}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.00,0:30:25.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,到酒馆里去！\N{\fs16}Into the tavern!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.37,0:30:35.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,快进酒馆！\N{\fs16}The tavern!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.62,0:30:38.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,全都进去！\N{\fs16}All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:42.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,快来！\N{\fs16}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.20,0:30:52.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,桌子！\N{\fs16}The table!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.62,0:30:55.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,快！\N{\fs16}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.91,0:31:11.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,快点！\N{\fs16}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.00,0:31:15.96,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈\N{\fs16}Mother. Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.37,0:31:22.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,先去救他\N{\fs16}Help him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.00,0:31:33.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不要啊\N{\fs16}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.70,0:31:35.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们会救你的\N{\fs16}We will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.83,0:31:38.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs16}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.16,0:31:39.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,希奥\N{\fs16}Theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.54,0:31:43.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你得赶紧止血\N{\fs16}You'll have to stem the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.62,0:31:44.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我 我不行\N{\fs16}I... I don't think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.91,0:31:48.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你要是做不到 我会死 你明白吗？\N{\fs16}Either you're gonna do this or I'm gonna die. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.87,0:31:52.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,希奥\N{\fs16}Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.12,0:32:07.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,母亲 做好准备\N{\fs16}Mother, prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.12,0:32:11.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,抱歉了\N{\fs16}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.95,0:32:25.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,快压住伤口\N{\fs16}Put pressure on the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.95,0:32:42.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,烧\N{\fs16}Burn...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.87,0:32:46.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,她好冷 她失血过多了\N{\fs16}She's cold. She's lost too much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.50,0:32:48.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\fs16}No. No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.16,0:32:49.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,她说「烧」\N{\fs16}"She's saying ""burn.""
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.08,0:32:53.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,用阿尔费琳种子 用火来烧结伤口\N{\fs16}The <i>alfirin</i> seeds. We have to seal the wound with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.62,0:32:55.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,拿些烧着的木头来 快！\N{\fs16}Bring me some burning wood. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.75,0:33:05.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs16}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.25,0:33:11.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,就是现在\N{\fs16}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.79,0:33:17.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,换这边\N{\fs16}Now this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.12,0:33:24.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\fs16}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.54,0:33:31.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,应该够了\N{\fs16}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:46.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,布隆玟？\N{\fs16}Bronwyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.91,0:33:49.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-母亲？-布隆玟？\N{\fs16}- Mother? - Bronwyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.75,0:33:51.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,醒醒！母亲！\N{\fs16}Wake up! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.29,0:34:27.37,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.50,0:34:30.08,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.16,0:34:31.25,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.91,0:34:34.00,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.45,0:34:36.54,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.95,0:34:39.29,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.37,0:34:41.45,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.16,0:34:44.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,从背后痛击他们！\N{\fs16}<i>Kick 'em in the back!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.58,0:34:46.62,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.16,0:34:49.16,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.83,0:34:51.87,Subtitle_LOTR-ORC,,0,0,0,,战斗！\N{\fs16}<i>Nampat!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.25,0:35:54.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,坐下！\N{\fs16}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.41,0:36:34.08,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,我要找的东西\N{\fs16}<i>Sana i cestan,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.16,0:36:35.83,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,把它给我\N{\fs16}<i>áse anta nin.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.16,0:36:38.58,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,放了他们\N{\fs16}<i>Áte sene...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.54,0:36:42.87,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,我会考虑\N{\fs16}<i>ar uvuvan sa.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.58,0:37:00.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,何必为如此微不足道的东西 赔上他们的性命？\N{\fs16}Why sacrifice their lives for such a little thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.41,0:37:22.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,那女人是下一个\N{\fs16}The woman next.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.29,0:37:25.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs16}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.04,0:37:32.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-等等！-希奥！\N{\fs16}- Wait! - Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.33,0:37:35.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,在地板下面\N{\fs16}It's under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.58,0:37:39.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,在地板下面\N{\fs16}It's under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.37,0:37:44.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs16}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.50,0:37:56.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,希奥！\N{\fs16}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.00,0:37:59.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs16}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.00,0:38:50.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,沃尔德雷格 我有件任务给你\N{\fs16}Waldreg, I have a task for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.62,0:39:01.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他们都得死\N{\fs16}They all must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.45,0:40:19.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,昂塔莫！\N{\fs16}Ontamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.45,0:40:49.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs16}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.41,0:40:51.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,驾！\N{\fs16}Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.87,0:41:02.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,驾！\N{\fs16}Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.20,0:41:18.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,父亲！\N{\fs16}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.54,0:41:30.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,父亲！\N{\fs16}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.12,0:41:32.28,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-我没事 -我以为你…\N{\fs16}- I'm all right. - I thought you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.25,0:41:34.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我没事 伊熙尔\N{\fs16}I'm all right, Isil.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.58,0:41:42.16,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,士兵\N{\fs16}<I>Mahtar.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.25,0:41:43.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,敌首何在？\N{\fs16}Their commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.62,0:41:49.06,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,他所持之物\N{\fs16}<i>I maryasse…</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.12,0:41:50.87,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,绝不可被他带走\N{\fs16}<i>vá usuva se asse.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:01.78,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,她是谁？\N{\fs16}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.41,0:42:07.09,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,北方军的指挥官\N{\fs16}Commander of the Northern Armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.41,0:42:09.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fs16}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.29,0:42:50.87,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,快跑！\N{\fs16}<i>Noro lim!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.87,0:43:20.95,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,快跑！\N{\fs16}<i>Noro lim!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.33,0:44:01.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,还记得我吗？\N{\fs16}You remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.50,0:44:09.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不记得\N{\fs16}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.45,0:44:24.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,住手！\N{\fs16}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.00,0:44:27.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们需要活口\N{\fs16}We need him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.87,0:44:29.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我需要活口\N{\fs16}I need him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.66,0:44:32.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你不知道他做了什么\N{\fs16}You don't know what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.58,0:44:41.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我给你爱的人带去伤痛了吗？\N{\fs16}Did I cause someone you love pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.54,0:44:46.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,一个女人？\N{\fs16}A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.04,0:44:54.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,或许是个孩子？\N{\fs16}Perhaps a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.33,0:44:55.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fs16}Eat your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.33,0:45:01.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,哈尔布兰德 放下武器\N{\fs16}Halbrand, put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.16,0:45:09.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,人不能饮海水止渴\N{\fs16}One cannot satisfy thirst by drinking sea water.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.70,0:45:29.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,所以 你感觉如何？\N{\fs16}So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.37,0:45:34.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这群山\N{\fs16}I like the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.08,0:45:38.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你马上就能更仔细地瞧瞧它们了\N{\fs16}You're about to get a closer look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.54,0:45:41.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,指挥官加拉德瑞尔要召集一支队伍\N{\fs16}Commander Galadriel's putting together a company
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.04,0:45:44.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,追踪逃走的奥克\N{\fs16}to track down the Orcs that escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.12,0:45:46.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,而我设法为我俩挣来了位置\N{\fs16}and I managed to wheedle the pair of us a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.75,0:45:47.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,昂塔莫呢？\N{\fs16}What about Ontamo?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.00,0:45:51.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我想我会在这儿待一阵 帮帮这群伙计\N{\fs16}I think I might stay here for a while. Lend these folk a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.54,0:45:55.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-受够了一周的战斗？-这辈子都够了\N{\fs16}- Seen enough battle for a week? - More like a whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.25,0:46:01.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这支队伍何时动身？\N{\fs16}This company, when's it set out?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.70,0:46:05.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,还不确定 得等她处置好他再说\N{\fs16}Don't know for certain. Not till she's done with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.54,0:46:15.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我孩童时期 听过精灵被魔苟斯带走的故事\N{\fs16}When I was a child, I heard stories of Elves taken by Morgoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.00,0:46:19.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他们被折磨 扭曲\N{\fs16}Tortured. Twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.87,0:46:24.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,被塑造成新的 被摧残的生命形式\N{\fs16}Made into a new and ruined form of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.58,0:46:29.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你也是其中一员 对吗？\N{\fs16}You are one of them, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.75,0:46:32.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,魔里昂多\N{\fs16}The Moriondor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.00,0:46:35.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,黑暗之子\N{\fs16}The Sons of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.83,0:46:38.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,最初的奥克\N{\fs16}The first Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.50,0:46:40.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,乌鲁克\N{\fs16}<i>Uruk.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.04,0:46:46.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我们更愿意自称「乌鲁克」\N{\fs16}"We prefer <i>""Uruk.""</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.54,0:46:50.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,即使是魔里昂多也要听从主上号令\N{\fs16}Even Moriondor take orders from a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.08,0:46:51.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我要找的正是你的主人\N{\fs16}And I seek yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.62,0:46:53.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他在何处？\N{\fs16}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.91,0:46:56.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,索隆在何处？\N{\fs16}Where is Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.08,0:47:09.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,或许我们该让囚犯晒晒太阳\N{\fs16}Perhaps we should bring our prisoners into the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.54,0:47:19.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,魔苟斯败退之后\N{\fs16}After Morgoth's defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.50,0:47:24.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你们称之为「索隆」的那位\N{\fs16}the one you call Sauron...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.79,0:47:31.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,致力于「治愈」中洲\N{\fs16}Devoted himself to healing Middle-earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.75,0:47:38.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,令被伤毁的大地重归完满与秩序\N{\fs16}bringing its ruined lands together in perfect order.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.83,0:47:43.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他试图创造出一种力量\N{\fs16}He sought to craft a power
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.70,0:47:48.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不局限于血肉之躯\N{\fs16}not of the flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.83,0:47:52.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,而是远超其上\N{\fs16}But over flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.70,0:47:56.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,来自幽界的力量\N{\fs16}A power of the Unseen World.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.16,0:48:03.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他尽力笼络追随者 一路北行\N{\fs16}He bid as many as he could to follow him far north.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.91,0:48:07.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,可尽管他竭尽所能\N{\fs16}But try as he might...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.00,0:48:11.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,仍缺少一样东西\N{\fs16}Something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.54,0:48:22.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,它隐藏在黑暗术法的阴影里\N{\fs16}<i>A shadow of dark knowledge</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.12,0:48:27.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,即便是他也无处找寻\N{\fs16}<i>that kept itself hidden, even from him.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.37,0:48:34.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,哪怕他的找寻之路已经鲜血淋漓\N{\fs16}<i>No matter how much blood he spilt in its pursuit.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.25,0:48:42.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,至于我\N{\fs16}Mmm. For my part...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.58,0:48:49.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,为了他的欲望 我已经牺牲了太多孩子\N{\fs16}I sacrificed enough of my children for his aspirations.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.50,0:48:55.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我将他开膛破腹\N{\fs16}I split him open.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.04,0:49:00.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我杀了索隆\N{\fs16}I killed Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.79,0:49:02.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我不信\N{\fs16}I do not believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.08,0:49:10.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你当然不信一个乌鲁克能杀了他\N{\fs16}You cannot believe an <i>Uruk</i> could do that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.29,0:49:14.45,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,毕竟你们整支大军都无法做到\N{\fs16}which your entire army could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.87,0:49:18.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我不相信你是这支军队唯一的主人\N{\fs16}I cannot believe that you are this army's only master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.95,0:49:21.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我的孩子没有主人\N{\fs16}My children have no master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.25,0:49:23.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他们不是孩子 他们是奴隶\N{\fs16}They are not children, they are slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.62,0:49:25.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,但他们每一个都有名字\N{\fs16}But each one has a name. A heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.25,0:49:28.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,都有心\N{\fs16}A heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.37,0:49:31.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-魔苟斯创造的心 -我们是独一之神的造物\N{\fs16}- A heart created by Morgoth. - We are creations of The One,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.66,0:49:34.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,出自秘火主宰之手 同你们一样\N{\fs16}Master of the Secret Fire, the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.95,0:49:37.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,他们值得这一息生命\N{\fs16}As worthy of the breath of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.33,0:49:41.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,也值得一个家\N{\fs16}and just as worthy of a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.16,0:49:46.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,很快\N{\fs16}Soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.70,0:49:51.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这片土地将属于我们 到那时你就会明白\N{\fs16}This land will be ours. Then, you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.87,0:49:59.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs16}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.29,0:50:04.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你们一族是个错误\N{\fs16}Your kind was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.83,0:50:07.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,是拙劣的仿品\N{\fs16}Made in mockery.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.29,0:50:14.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,哪怕要花上整个纪元 我也发誓要将你们铲除殆尽\N{\fs16}And even if it takes me all of this Age, I vow to eradicate every last one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.45,0:50:21.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,但我会留你一命\N{\fs16}But you shall be kept alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.25,0:50:23.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,等到那一天\N{\fs16}so that one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.95,0:50:26.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,在我的匕首刺入你腐坏的心脏之前\N{\fs16}before I drive my dagger into your poisoned heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.16,0:50:31.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我会在你的尖耳朵旁低语\N{\fs16}I will whisper in your piked ear
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.25,0:50:33.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,说你的后代无一存活\N{\fs16}that all your offspring are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.08,0:50:38.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你们一族的祸根于你终结\N{\fs16}and the scourge of your kind ends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.04,0:50:46.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,看来我不是唯一一个活着\N{\fs16}It would seem I'm not the only Elf alive
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.50,0:50:49.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,却已经被黑暗转化的精灵\N{\fs16}who has been transformed by darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.79,0:50:54.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,也许你所寻觅的魔苟斯的继任者\N{\fs16}Perhaps your search for Morgoth's successor
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.37,0:50:56.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,最终会出现在你的镜中倒影里\N{\fs16}should have ended in your own mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.70,0:51:01.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,也许我该先杀了你 你这流涎的奥克\N{\fs16}Perhaps I shall begin by killing you, you slavering Orc.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.50,0:51:02.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fs16}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.58,0:51:09.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,乌鲁克\N{\fs16}<i>Uruk.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.37,0:51:38.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fs16}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.12,0:52:19.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs16}Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.16,0:52:22.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,把我拉了回来\N{\fs16}For pulling me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.79,0:52:27.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,之前是你把我拉了回来\N{\fs16}Was you, pulled me back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.50,0:52:34.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不管他对你做了什么\N{\fs16}Whatever it was he did to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.87,0:52:37.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,也不管你做了什么\N{\fs16}and whatever it was you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.58,0:52:43.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,都要放下\N{\fs16}Be free of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.66,0:52:48.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我从没觉得我能放下\N{\fs16}I never believed I could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.08,0:52:56.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,直到今天\N{\fs16}Until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.95,0:53:04.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,与你并肩作战 我\N{\fs16}Fighting at your side, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.29,0:53:07.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\fs16}I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.25,0:53:12.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,如果我能抓住这种感觉\N{\fs16}If I could just hold on to that feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.12,0:53:16.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,时刻带在身边\N{\fs16}keep it with me always,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.04,0:53:22.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,将它与我的灵魂紧紧相连 那么我\N{\fs16}bind it to my very being, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.54,0:53:27.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我也有同样的感受\N{\fs16}I felt it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.66,0:53:43.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,哈尔布兰德大人\N{\fs16}Lord Halbrand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.08,0:53:45.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,执政女王想要见您\N{\fs16}The Queen Regent wishes to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.91,0:54:42.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,执政女王\N{\fs16}Queen Regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.41,0:54:52.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我欠你的 我的族人因你才得以生存\N{\fs16}What I owe you... My people are alive because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.00,0:54:56.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,在我看来 他们能活下来是因为你\N{\fs16}As I understand it, they're alive because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.00,0:54:59.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我从未想过要背负这样的重担\N{\fs16}A burden I never sought to take up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.83,0:55:03.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,那些最优秀的领袖也是一样\N{\fs16}Few of the finest leaders do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.04,0:55:12.50,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不过 如果你想减轻一点负担\N{\fs16}But if you would like some relief in carrying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.70,0:55:15.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,或许我可以帮忙\N{\fs16}I may be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.66,0:55:18.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,您在找我 殿下？\N{\fs16}You called for me, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.91,0:55:21.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,布隆玟\N{\fs16}Bronwyn...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.58,0:55:24.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这位是哈尔布兰德大人\N{\fs16}This is Lord Halbrand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.95,0:55:38.12,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,布隆玟\N{\fs16}Bronwyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.25,0:55:44.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,是真的吗？你就是我们应许的国王？\N{\fs16}Is it true? Are you the king we were promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.66,0:55:56.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs16}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.20,0:56:03.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,致敬吧！\N{\fs16}All hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.37,0:56:09.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,向真正的南境之王致敬！\N{\fs16}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.33,0:56:13.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,向真正的南境之王致敬！\N{\fs16}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.87,0:56:17.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,向真正的南境之王致敬！\N{\fs16}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.91,0:56:26.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,这片土地上的人们等待这一刻很久了\N{\fs16}The men of these lands have awaited this moment a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.87,0:56:29.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,远不及精灵等得久\N{\fs16}Not nearly so long as the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.83,0:57:06.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不要折磨自己了\N{\fs16}Do not torment yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.29,0:57:13.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,在那种处境下 很多人都会这么做\N{\fs16}Many might have done the same in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.70,0:57:22.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你不懂\N{\fs16}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.95,0:57:28.16,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是愧疚\N{\fs16}It's not just guilt I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.83,0:57:33.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,还有失落\N{\fs16}It's loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.91,0:57:37.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,失落？\N{\fs16}Loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.25,0:57:44.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,当它在我手中\N{\fs16}When it was in my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.37,0:57:47.54,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我感受到了\N{\fs16}I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.70,0:57:52.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,力量\N{\fs16}Powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.08,0:57:58.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,那就摆脱它吧\N{\fs16}Then rid yourself of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.08,0:58:02.58,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,彻底摆脱\N{\fs16}Once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.20,0:58:04.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,怎么做？\N{\fs16}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.33,0:58:08.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,把它交给努门诺尔人\N{\fs16}Give it to Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.70,0:58:12.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,让他们在返乡途中丢进大海\N{\fs16}To toss into the sea on their voyage home.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.70,0:59:47.41,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,冷静点 贝瑞克 冷静\N{\fs16}Easy. Berek, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.25,0:59:51.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,只是擦伤 没事的\N{\fs16}It's just a scratch. You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.12,0:59:53.75,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,嘿 贝瑞克\N{\fs16}Hey, hey, hey. Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.62,0:59:56.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\fs16}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.20,1:00:03.75,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,安静点\N{\fs16}<i>Athae… no ídhui hí.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.25,1:00:09.70,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你怎么做到的？\N{\fs16}How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.79,1:00:12.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,困扰它的并不是自身的疼痛\N{\fs16}It's not his pain that's bothering him...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.50,1:00:14.83,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,而是骑手的\N{\fs16}But that of his rider.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.91,1:00:17.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,我并不觉得疼痛\N{\fs16}I'm not in pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.00,1:00:21.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,当西方之地的马踏上战场\N{\fs16}When a horse of Westernesse rides into battle,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.79,1:00:27.29,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,就会与它的骑手建立牢不可破的羁绊\N{\fs16}he forms an unbreakable bond with the soldier he bears.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.12,1:00:30.25,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,渐渐地 他们合二为一\N{\fs16}In time, they become as one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.33,1:00:33.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,甚至通晓彼此内心最深处的感受\N{\fs16}Even knowing the innermost feelings of each other's heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.04,1:00:36.66,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,-你知道它的感受？ -不\N{\fs16}- You know his feelings? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.62,1:00:38.79,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,它知道你的\N{\fs16}He knows yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.29,1:00:44.04,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你从哪里学到这些的？\N{\fs16}Where did you learn all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.58,1:00:48.00,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,从你的母亲那里\N{\fs16}From your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.58,1:00:59.08,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,你可以教我吗？\N{\fs16}Think you could teach me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.12,1:01:40.33,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,乌顿\N{\fs16}<i>Udûn...</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.41,1:01:43.62,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,乌顿 乌顿\N{\fs16}<i>Udûn. Udûn.</i>
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.12,1:03:27.20,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,找掩护！\N{\fs16}Take shelter!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.87,1:03:31.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,女王！\N{\fs16}The Queen!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.87,1:03:37.87,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,贝瑞克！\N{\fs16}Berek!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.75,1:03:41.95,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,维蓝迪尔！\N{\fs16}Valandil!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.70,1:04:05.91,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,去墙那儿！\N{\fs16}Over the wall!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.00,1:04:08.37,Subtitle - LOTR-TROPstandard,,0,0,0,,希奥！希奥！\N{\fs16}- Theo! - Theo!
Comment: 0,0:37:47.50,0:37:48.50,Subtitle_LOTR-ELF,,0,0,0,,阿隆迪尔\N{\fs16}Arondir.

